          <h1>Living Off Campus</h1>
          <h2 style = "width:92%">
            The Off Campus Student Center is an on-campus home for off-campus students. The Center is located in room 314 of the Student Union and is staffed by Off Campus Student Life Coordinators, Graduate Assistants, and professional staff. These individuals act as a resource for students who live or plan to live off campus.
