            Walk This Way encourages students to walk on campus rather than along residential streets as they move to and from the Southwest Residential Area. Many neighbors and students have felt the impact of noise, trash, public urination, and vandalism on weekend evenings.
            <br><br>
            The goal of Walk This Way is to encourage students to change their path away from the neighborhoods to minimize this impact while reminding students who choose to walk in the neighborhoods to be mindful of their noise level.
